[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,460 --> 00:01:41,000
[Strange Tales of Tang Dynasty II To the West]

3
00:01:41,470 --> 00:01:43,870
[Episode 27]

4
00:01:46,020 --> 00:01:47,140
Let go of me!

5
00:01:50,710 --> 00:01:51,390
Let go!

6
00:02:00,310 --> 00:02:01,570
Qing Fu drew it for you?

7
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:03,510
Miss Peony,

8
00:02:03,710 --> 00:02:05,230
you're so fair-skinned

9
00:02:05,260 --> 00:02:06,150
You bastard!

10
00:02:06,590 --> 00:02:07,210
I am a bastard.

11
00:02:07,210 --> 00:02:08,570
I am indeed a bastard!

12
00:02:09,509 --> 00:02:10,190
Go away!

13
00:02:11,150 --> 00:02:11,900
Go away!

14
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:13,130
Don't bully Qing Xi,

15
00:02:13,410 --> 00:02:14,700
or else I'll kill you!

16
00:02:18,270 --> 00:02:19,230
Who are you?

17
00:02:19,540 --> 00:02:20,960
It's none of your business who I am.

18
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:22,070
I'll kill you!

19
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:45,990
Wang Qiu,

20
00:02:46,500 --> 00:02:46,910
you...

21
00:02:47,950 --> 00:02:49,079
You killed someone.

22
00:02:52,740 --> 00:02:54,070
After I killed that guy,

23
00:02:55,050 --> 00:02:56,650
I told Qing Xi to leave first.

24
00:02:57,900 --> 00:02:58,760
Unexpectedly,

25
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,550
she didn't go home.

26
00:03:03,060 --> 00:03:05,350
Something must have happened to her on the way.

27
00:03:05,350 --> 00:03:06,450
Why didn't you leave

28
00:03:06,450 --> 00:03:07,710
together with Qing Xi?

29
00:03:08,950 --> 00:03:09,680
At that time,

30
00:03:10,590 --> 00:03:12,720
I hadn't recovered from the shock yet.

31
00:03:12,900 --> 00:03:14,370
I couldn't believe I had killed someone.

32
00:03:14,370 --> 00:03:16,100
How did you hack Wu Cai to death?

33
00:03:16,829 --> 00:03:18,100
With a knife, of course.

34
00:03:18,100 --> 00:03:19,270
How else could I do it?

35
00:03:19,270 --> 00:03:21,200
Which part of the body did you hack?

36
00:03:21,300 --> 00:03:22,500
I hacked him randomly

37
00:03:22,790 --> 00:03:24,550
and finally hacked the back of his head.

38
00:03:24,550 --> 00:03:26,550
Did you do it with the knife's blade?

39
00:03:27,550 --> 00:03:28,140
Yes.

40
00:03:30,090 --> 00:03:32,150
How many hacks did it take to kill him?

41
00:03:33,910 --> 00:03:35,400
About two or three hacks.

42
00:03:36,150 --> 00:03:37,230
He couldn't hold up

43
00:03:38,630 --> 00:03:39,430
and died.

44
00:03:45,130 --> 00:03:47,280
Why are you still lying?

45
00:03:48,030 --> 00:03:48,430
I…

46
00:03:49,230 --> 00:03:50,070
I'm not.

47
00:03:50,630 --> 00:03:52,070
I've already admitted that I killed him.

48
00:03:52,070 --> 00:03:53,800
How can you still say I'm lying?

49
00:03:54,030 --> 00:03:55,270
Do you know who he is?

50
00:03:57,030 --> 00:03:57,829
He is the best

51
00:03:58,270 --> 00:03:59,910
forensic expert in the country.

52
00:03:59,910 --> 00:04:00,980
Perk up your ears

53
00:04:01,230 --> 00:04:02,490
and listen carefully.

54
00:04:03,110 --> 00:04:04,190
On the side of the neck,

55
00:04:04,190 --> 00:04:06,560
there are two arc-shaped marks

56
00:04:06,870 --> 00:04:08,130
and there is bleeding.

57
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:10,110
It's clearly a bite mark

58
00:04:10,390 --> 00:04:12,230
and the bite was very strong.

59
00:04:12,630 --> 00:04:14,710
On the lower back of his head,

60
00:04:14,730 --> 00:04:15,960
the scalp is split open

61
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:17,480
from the bottom to the top.

62
00:04:17,500 --> 00:04:19,510
It should be an injury caused by a blunt object.

63
00:04:19,510 --> 00:04:23,260
There are multiple knife injuries from the neck to the back.

64
00:04:24,630 --> 00:04:25,790
As you described,

65
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:28,830
the bite marks on the neck

66
00:04:28,850 --> 00:04:31,910
should have been left by Qing Xi when she was resisting.

67
00:04:32,310 --> 00:04:33,200
However,

68
00:04:33,690 --> 00:04:36,010
the mass of knife wounds

69
00:04:36,150 --> 00:04:38,310
from the back of Wu Cai's head to his neck

70
00:04:38,310 --> 00:04:39,200
are actually

71
00:04:39,390 --> 00:04:41,300
divided into two parts.

72
00:04:42,590 --> 00:04:44,950
Close to the neck,

73
00:04:45,550 --> 00:04:47,510
there is a wound

74
00:04:47,870 --> 00:04:49,270
with the flesh split open

75
00:04:49,310 --> 00:04:52,150
from the bottom to the top.

76
00:04:52,590 --> 00:04:54,450
It wasn't caused by a sharp blade.

77
00:04:54,590 --> 00:04:56,150
You can't create such a wound

78
00:04:56,150 --> 00:04:58,190
with a knife's blade.

79
00:05:01,430 --> 00:05:01,950
This...

80
00:05:02,170 --> 00:05:04,050
You are still lying.

81
00:05:04,950 --> 00:05:05,950
It's very unwise.

82
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:08,040
This Sheriff Lu

83
00:05:08,630 --> 00:05:10,230
is very famous.

84
00:05:10,490 --> 00:05:12,420
Even the bandits of Chang'an and Luoyang

85
00:05:12,420 --> 00:05:13,190
all fear him.

86
00:05:13,430 --> 00:05:14,990
He just took office in Yunding

87
00:05:14,990 --> 00:05:16,610
and is in the midst of establishing his authority.

88
00:05:16,610 --> 00:05:18,870
Have you thought about the consequences

89
00:05:18,870 --> 00:05:20,470
of angering him at this time?

90
00:05:26,550 --> 00:05:27,950
I didn't kill the person.

91
00:05:28,420 --> 00:05:29,430
It was Qing Xi.

92
00:05:30,550 --> 00:05:31,230
Honey.

93
00:05:31,230 --> 00:05:32,270
Let go of me!

94
00:05:32,590 --> 00:05:34,040
-Let go of me!
-Don’t bully Qingxi,

95
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:35,510
or else I'll kill you!

96
00:05:52,440 --> 00:05:53,370
Who allowed you?

97
00:05:53,750 --> 00:05:54,680
Who allowed you?

98
00:05:55,430 --> 00:05:56,630
I'll kill you.

99
00:05:56,909 --> 00:05:57,950
You little brat.

100
00:05:58,710 --> 00:05:59,350
You-

101
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:01,090
I'll kill you!

102
00:06:09,980 --> 00:06:10,550
Qing Xi.

103
00:06:12,110 --> 00:06:12,970
You killed him.

104
00:06:16,620 --> 00:06:18,550
How many times did Qing Xi hack him?

105
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:19,310
I...

106
00:06:20,070 --> 00:06:20,830
At that time,

107
00:06:22,070 --> 00:06:24,470
I was about to pass out from the strangling.

108
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:25,840
I didn't see clearly.

109
00:06:26,260 --> 00:06:27,520
It should be one slash.

110
00:06:27,750 --> 00:06:28,670
Or maybe two.

111
00:06:30,110 --> 00:06:31,910
It's also possible that it was three.

112
00:06:31,910 --> 00:06:35,040
It's easy to suffocate when being strangled by the neck.

113
00:06:35,230 --> 00:06:37,990
It's understandable that you couldn't see clearly.

114
00:06:37,990 --> 00:06:39,600
Then let me rephrase the question.

115
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:41,730
Did Qing Xi

116
00:06:41,750 --> 00:06:43,409
hack Wu Cai's neck

117
00:06:43,750 --> 00:06:44,950
in a frenzy?

118
00:06:46,620 --> 00:06:47,480
No, she didn't.

119
00:06:48,950 --> 00:06:49,680
Are you sure?

120
00:06:53,810 --> 00:06:54,720
I'm not sure.

121
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:57,290
Qing Xi,

122
00:06:57,750 --> 00:06:59,100
I'm sorry.

123
00:07:00,190 --> 00:07:00,890
I originally

124
00:07:00,890 --> 00:07:02,990
wanted to take the death penalty for you.

125
00:07:02,990 --> 00:07:04,270
But I failed

126
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:06,110
this important matter.

127
00:07:06,830 --> 00:07:07,430
Alright,

128
00:07:07,670 --> 00:07:08,550
stop crying.

129
00:07:09,650 --> 00:07:11,150
Where is the knife?

130
00:07:12,500 --> 00:07:13,100
It just...

131
00:07:13,870 --> 00:07:14,930
fell on the ground.

132
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:16,740
You didn't take it?

133
00:07:27,220 --> 00:07:27,880
Sheriff Lu,

134
00:07:28,670 --> 00:07:29,960
your cooperation with Mr. Su

135
00:07:29,960 --> 00:07:31,290
is truly seamless.

136
00:07:31,820 --> 00:07:33,030
I've learned a lot.

137
00:07:33,050 --> 00:07:34,580
Stop flattering me for now.

138
00:07:35,190 --> 00:07:36,710
Let's bring Wang Qiu with us

139
00:07:36,710 --> 00:07:38,850
and retrace the route he took last night

140
00:07:38,850 --> 00:07:40,110
when following Qing Xi

141
00:07:40,300 --> 00:07:41,900
all the way to Wu Cai's house.

142
00:07:42,070 --> 00:07:42,870
Then we'll see

143
00:07:43,430 --> 00:07:44,820
if he was lying or not.

144
00:07:45,260 --> 00:07:45,830
Alright.

145
00:07:49,940 --> 00:07:51,670
You want to take Wang Qiu

146
00:07:52,030 --> 00:07:54,090
and retrace the path from last night?

147
00:07:54,870 --> 00:07:55,900
You guessed it.

148
00:07:57,100 --> 00:07:58,990
The shopkeeper of the bookstore said

149
00:07:58,990 --> 00:08:01,850
Qing Xi was in a great hurry when returning the book.

150
00:08:01,900 --> 00:08:04,210
In the hour when Wang Qiu lost track of her,

151
00:08:04,210 --> 00:08:05,740
what exactly was she doing?

152
00:08:06,150 --> 00:08:07,950
It may be irrelevant to this case,

153
00:08:07,950 --> 00:08:09,480
but I still want to find out.

154
00:08:10,070 --> 00:08:11,710
Do you want to come along?

155
00:08:12,510 --> 00:08:14,950
From Wang Qiu's confession,

156
00:08:14,990 --> 00:08:18,910
it's possible that Qing Xi may flee to escape punishment,

157
00:08:18,910 --> 00:08:19,580
so

158
00:08:19,990 --> 00:08:22,480
I want to go and take a look at Bao Kang's home.

159
00:08:26,430 --> 00:08:27,070
Bao Kang?

160
00:08:31,030 --> 00:08:32,390
Is Bao Kang here?

161
00:08:51,270 --> 00:08:51,800
Bao Kang?

162
00:09:09,970 --> 00:09:11,900
I was calling you from downstairs.

163
00:09:12,030 --> 00:09:13,470
Why didn't you answer?

164
00:09:14,230 --> 00:09:15,560
What's there to answer?

165
00:09:15,950 --> 00:09:18,430
I am working under Lu Lingfeng,

166
00:09:18,470 --> 00:09:20,400
the new sheriff of Yunding County.

167
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:21,710
I'm visiting late at night

168
00:09:21,710 --> 00:09:23,840
because I have some questions for you.

169
00:09:27,310 --> 00:09:28,670
What's there to ask?

170
00:09:29,830 --> 00:09:31,800
Your wife, Qing Xi,

171
00:09:31,830 --> 00:09:34,230
has been missing for a day and a night,

172
00:09:34,710 --> 00:09:36,630
yet you're so unconcerned.

173
00:09:37,260 --> 00:09:38,990
It'd be better if she were dead.

174
00:09:42,910 --> 00:09:44,510
I heard from Sheriff Lu

175
00:09:44,710 --> 00:09:48,070
that you and Qing Xi sleep in separate beds,

176
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:51,990
but you don't admit to marital discord.

177
00:09:53,910 --> 00:09:54,570
Why is that?

178
00:09:55,230 --> 00:09:58,250
Could there be some unspeakable difficulty?

179
00:09:59,590 --> 00:10:01,160
What's it to you?

180
00:10:06,070 --> 00:10:08,910
You've indeed had misfortune.

181
00:10:09,800 --> 00:10:11,950
You used to be able to go into the mountains to gather herbs,

182
00:10:11,950 --> 00:10:15,030
but now, you're bedridden.

183
00:10:15,830 --> 00:10:16,910
Just tell me,

184
00:10:18,540 --> 00:10:19,560
when will you

185
00:10:19,580 --> 00:10:21,120
help me find Qing Xi?

186
00:10:21,290 --> 00:10:22,150
Didn't you just

187
00:10:22,150 --> 00:10:23,350
curse her to die?

188
00:10:23,890 --> 00:10:25,720
I was just speaking out of anger.

189
00:10:27,830 --> 00:10:28,890
Then let me ask you.

190
00:10:28,990 --> 00:10:31,030
Before Qing Xi went missing,

191
00:10:31,150 --> 00:10:33,280
was there anything unusual about her?

192
00:10:34,070 --> 00:10:34,790
No.

193
00:10:35,430 --> 00:10:38,010
After you broke your leg, did she complain

194
00:10:38,300 --> 00:10:39,700
while taking care of you?

195
00:10:39,830 --> 00:10:42,280
Why are you asking about this?

196
00:10:42,500 --> 00:10:44,700
There are two types of disappearances.

197
00:10:45,060 --> 00:10:46,650
One is an involuntary disappearance.

198
00:10:46,650 --> 00:10:48,730
The other is voluntary.

199
00:10:49,350 --> 00:10:51,000
The case is unclear at present.

200
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:53,230
We can't rule out

201
00:10:53,350 --> 00:10:56,010
the possibility of a voluntary disappearance.

202
00:10:58,150 --> 00:10:58,950
Are you saying

203
00:10:59,750 --> 00:11:01,810
Qing Xi didn't want to take care of me,

204
00:11:02,550 --> 00:11:03,470
so she ran away?

205
00:11:04,160 --> 00:11:05,320
Based on how mean

206
00:11:05,350 --> 00:11:06,730
you sounded just now,

207
00:11:07,110 --> 00:11:08,600
it's a possibility.

208
00:11:25,700 --> 00:11:26,550
Tell me,

209
00:11:27,500 --> 00:11:29,550
how did you get injured?

210
00:11:32,590 --> 00:11:34,990
That day, I was tired from gathering herbs.

211
00:11:35,750 --> 00:11:37,150
I drank a gourd of wine

212
00:11:38,350 --> 00:11:40,410
and fell asleep on the edge of a cliff.

213
00:11:41,990 --> 00:11:43,710
Unexpectedly, a tiger came.

214
00:11:44,140 --> 00:11:46,200
When it sniffed my face with its nose,

215
00:11:47,740 --> 00:11:49,800
its whiskers poked into my nostrils.

216
00:11:50,490 --> 00:11:51,710
I sneezed,

217
00:11:52,190 --> 00:11:53,650
which startled the tiger,

218
00:11:54,590 --> 00:11:56,050
but I was even more scared.

219
00:11:56,190 --> 00:11:58,590
I actually forgot I was on the edge of a cliff

220
00:11:59,110 --> 00:12:00,590
and tumbled down.

221
00:12:02,950 --> 00:12:04,230
I see.

222
00:12:07,810 --> 00:12:08,940
What a coincidence.

223
00:12:09,910 --> 00:12:12,960
I have a friend named Fei Yingjun.

224
00:12:13,630 --> 00:12:15,670
He's a disciple of the King of Medicine.

225
00:12:15,670 --> 00:12:16,720
He's practically a miracle doctor.

226
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:18,030
I'll call him over tomorrow

227
00:12:18,030 --> 00:12:19,120
to take a look at you.

228
00:12:19,120 --> 00:12:21,450
Even if an immortal came, it'd be useless.

229
00:12:22,150 --> 00:12:23,650
I broke my leg.

230
00:12:24,380 --> 00:12:25,590
It can't be healed.

231
00:12:26,490 --> 00:12:28,150
You don't want to get treated?

232
00:12:29,950 --> 00:12:31,550
It's not that I don't want to.

233
00:12:32,450 --> 00:12:34,030
I've been gathering herbs for so many years.

234
00:12:34,030 --> 00:12:36,870
Don't you think I know how to treat injuries from falls?

235
00:12:36,870 --> 00:12:39,310
It's just a pity that the injury is too severe.

236
00:12:39,310 --> 00:12:40,430
It can't be cured.

237
00:12:43,950 --> 00:12:45,230
Is this your cat?

238
00:12:47,310 --> 00:12:48,840
It's quite pretty.

239
00:12:56,390 --> 00:12:57,830
Don't scare my cat.

240
00:13:01,300 --> 00:13:03,360
It doesn't have a guilty conscience.

241
00:13:04,580 --> 00:13:05,780
It's not afraid of me.

242
00:13:26,390 --> 00:13:28,050
I heard Wang Qiu was arrested.

243
00:13:28,390 --> 00:13:28,990
Qing Xi

244
00:13:29,350 --> 00:13:30,910
was killed by him, right?

245
00:13:35,350 --> 00:13:38,070
If this kind of talk spreads,

246
00:13:38,230 --> 00:13:40,760
the county government will punish you for it.

247
00:13:41,750 --> 00:13:43,280
What are you talking about?

248
00:13:43,350 --> 00:13:44,070
My lips

249
00:13:44,390 --> 00:13:45,430
are sealed.

250
00:13:45,860 --> 00:13:46,770
All the neighbors

251
00:13:46,770 --> 00:13:48,140
know that.

252
00:13:49,630 --> 00:13:50,590
Your Honor,

253
00:13:50,890 --> 00:13:52,220
are the clues I provided

254
00:13:52,310 --> 00:13:53,150
useful?

255
00:13:54,310 --> 00:13:55,640
They are indeed useful.

256
00:13:56,140 --> 00:13:58,060
Now that Wang Qiu has been arrested,

257
00:13:58,060 --> 00:13:59,550
let someone from my side

258
00:13:59,820 --> 00:14:01,080
take care of Bao Kang.

259
00:14:02,150 --> 00:14:03,870
You know the county government

260
00:14:03,870 --> 00:14:05,840
will pay for it, right?

261
00:14:06,790 --> 00:14:09,620
I'm just trying to relieve the county government's worries.

262
00:14:09,620 --> 00:14:11,620
Let my husband take care of Bao Kang.

263
00:14:12,030 --> 00:14:13,220
Isn't that much better

264
00:14:13,220 --> 00:14:14,140
than that kid?

265
00:14:14,270 --> 00:14:15,150
Your husband?

266
00:14:15,650 --> 00:14:16,920
I remember you said

267
00:14:16,950 --> 00:14:17,940
you were a widow.

268
00:14:18,160 --> 00:14:19,910
I am a widow,

269
00:14:21,110 --> 00:14:22,770
but now I have a husband again.

270
00:14:23,630 --> 00:14:25,150
Is this contradictory?

271
00:14:26,150 --> 00:14:27,080
It's not,

272
00:14:27,750 --> 00:14:28,840
but Bao Kang

273
00:14:29,190 --> 00:14:31,720
doesn't need your husband to take care of him.

274
00:14:32,430 --> 00:14:33,310
Stingy.

275
00:14:33,590 --> 00:14:34,510
If I had known it would be like this,

276
00:14:34,510 --> 00:14:36,240
I should have told the sheriff.

277
00:14:36,400 --> 00:14:37,500
You're just a follower.

278
00:14:37,500 --> 00:14:39,430
What you say doesn't count anyway.

279
00:14:47,740 --> 00:14:48,350
Right here

280
00:14:48,790 --> 00:14:50,250
is where I lost Qing Xi.

281
00:14:50,670 --> 00:14:52,190
It's the two intersections up ahead.

282
00:14:52,190 --> 00:14:54,390
I didn't see clearly which way she went.

283
00:15:04,900 --> 00:15:05,560
Squat down.

284
00:15:19,910 --> 00:15:20,710
Wang Qiu,

285
00:15:21,230 --> 00:15:22,830
what was with you yesterday?

286
00:15:25,530 --> 00:15:27,670
I knew that woman

287
00:15:27,710 --> 00:15:28,780
you were following.

288
00:15:28,780 --> 00:15:30,150
I didn't expect you

289
00:15:30,230 --> 00:15:32,130
