305
00:16:12,110 --> 00:16:12,790
Jin Bao?

306
00:16:13,750 --> 00:16:14,610
That huntsman?

307
00:16:14,630 --> 00:16:15,190
Yes, yes.

308
00:16:15,670 --> 00:16:16,670
He's my neighbor.

309
00:16:18,990 --> 00:16:19,450
Friend,

310
00:16:19,890 --> 00:16:20,480
not bad.

311
00:16:26,460 --> 00:16:27,020
Qing Xi,

312
00:16:27,080 --> 00:16:27,880
what's wrong?

313
00:16:30,390 --> 00:16:30,780
Here.

314
00:16:31,840 --> 00:16:32,550
Jin Bao?

315
00:16:32,910 --> 00:16:33,960
Bao Kang treated him as a friend,

316
00:16:33,960 --> 00:16:35,110
but he used such tactics

317
00:16:35,110 --> 00:16:36,170
