318
00:16:37,300 --> 00:16:38,100
This bastard.

319
00:16:41,590 --> 00:16:42,190
Oh, right.

320
00:16:42,310 --> 00:16:43,170
I remember now.

321
00:16:44,550 --> 00:16:45,210
Yesterday,

322
00:16:45,480 --> 00:16:47,010
I lost track of Qing Xi here.

323
00:16:47,510 --> 00:16:49,310
She must have gone to Jin Bao's house.

324
00:16:49,310 --> 00:16:50,510
What took you so long?

325
00:16:56,270 --> 00:16:57,590
Qing Xi went missing?

326
00:16:59,540 --> 00:17:01,400
She came to your house last night.

327
00:17:02,110 --> 00:17:02,970
No, she didn't.

328
00:17:03,970 --> 00:17:05,069
But at dusk yesterday,

329
00:17:05,069 --> 00:17:06,069
I did see her.

330
00:17:06,670 --> 00:17:08,829
There was a robber who tried to snatch her purse.

331
00:17:08,829 --> 00:17:09,960
I lent a helping hand

332
00:17:09,990 --> 00:17:11,589
