337
00:17:19,589 --> 00:17:20,319
Officer Suo.

338
00:17:25,470 --> 00:17:26,630
Is this the robber?

339
00:17:27,540 --> 00:17:28,030
This...

340
00:17:30,150 --> 00:17:30,950
Take him away.

341
00:17:34,140 --> 00:17:35,510
I... I did ask Huang You

342
00:17:35,510 --> 00:17:37,040
to pretend to be the robber.

343
00:17:37,390 --> 00:17:38,440
It's because

344
00:17:38,470 --> 00:17:40,130
Bao Kang and I had a falling out

345
00:17:40,550 --> 00:17:42,190
and I hadn't seen Qing Xi in a long time.

346
00:17:42,190 --> 00:17:43,190
I had no excuse

347
00:17:44,150 --> 00:17:46,510
and felt embarrassed to give her the pheasant directly.

348
00:17:46,510 --> 00:17:48,550
She clearly came to your house last night.

349
00:17:48,550 --> 00:17:49,750
Why are you hiding it?

350
00:17:50,670 --> 00:17:51,600
She didn't come.

351
00:17:52,070 --> 00:17:53,630
You're not telling the truth.

352
00:17:53,630 --> 00:17:54,150
Do you want me to

353
00:17:54,150 --> 00:17:55,550
