354
00:18:00,750 --> 00:18:01,270
Jin Bao,

355
00:18:01,630 --> 00:18:02,780
return Qing Xi to me!

356
00:18:03,310 --> 00:18:04,910
Last night, Qing Xi left home

357
00:18:05,510 --> 00:18:07,150
and Wang Qiu followed her all the way.

358
00:18:07,150 --> 00:18:09,550
