363
00:18:14,350 --> 00:18:14,880
I didn't.

364
00:18:15,630 --> 00:18:15,990
I...

365
00:18:17,630 --> 00:18:18,430
I'll confess.

366
00:18:19,990 --> 00:18:20,790
I'll confess.

367
00:18:23,070 --> 00:18:24,530
