371
00:18:31,740 --> 00:18:32,200
Go.

372
00:18:37,870 --> 00:18:38,710
So you…

373
00:18:39,270 --> 00:18:40,800
You must tell the truth now.

374
00:18:42,440 --> 00:18:44,240
I had Huang You pretend to rob her

375
00:18:44,750 --> 00:18:46,350
and then gave her a pheasant.

376
00:18:46,990 --> 00:18:48,790
I thought that Qing Xi was polite

377
00:18:49,430 --> 00:18:50,960
and would return the favor,

378
00:18:51,060 --> 00:18:52,190
so last night,

379
00:18:52,630 --> 00:18:54,290
I kept waiting for her at home.

380
00:18:59,230 --> 00:18:59,870
Qing Xi?

381
00:19:00,920 --> 00:19:01,520
Come on in.

382
00:19:02,390 --> 00:19:03,430
Come, have a seat.

383
00:19:05,670 --> 00:19:06,310
