390
00:19:27,830 --> 00:19:29,030
and vented his anger.

391
00:19:29,080 --> 00:19:29,880
It's nothing.

392
00:19:31,710 --> 00:19:33,370
A wife who is so understanding

393
00:19:33,670 --> 00:19:35,270
