394
00:19:35,750 --> 00:19:37,310
You haven't eaten yet, right?

395
00:19:37,310 --> 00:19:38,450
I just stewed the wild game.

396
00:19:38,450 --> 00:19:39,510
Try my cooking.

397
00:19:39,630 --> 00:19:40,200
No need.

398
00:19:40,700 --> 00:19:42,030
Don't stand on ceremony.

399
00:19:42,030 --> 00:19:43,910
I often ate your cooking before.

400
00:19:44,270 --> 00:19:45,800
Consider this a repayment.

401
00:19:49,000 --> 00:19:50,980
How did you meet

402
00:19:51,270 --> 00:19:52,500
Bao Kang and Qing Xi?

403
00:19:57,340 --> 00:19:58,270
Three years ago,

404
00:19:59,960 --> 00:20:01,760
when I was chasing a wild rabbit,

405
00:20:02,720 --> 00:20:03,960
I accidentally slipped down

406
00:20:03,960 --> 00:20:04,790
a hill

407
00:20:05,310 --> 00:20:06,510
and twisted my ankle.

408
00:20:06,800 --> 00:20:07,670
Luckily, Bao Kang was

409
00:20:07,670 --> 00:20:09,800
collecting herbs nearby and found me.

410
00:20:10,310 --> 00:20:11,310
He treated my injury

411
00:20:11,310 --> 00:20:12,630
and helped me down the mountain.

412
00:20:12,630 --> 00:20:13,690
After I recovered,

413
00:20:14,030 --> 00:20:15,250
we often went into the mountains

414
00:20:15,250 --> 00:20:16,130
together.

415
00:20:17,310 --> 00:20:18,350
He would collect herbs

416
00:20:18,350 --> 00:20:19,280
and I would hunt.

417
00:20:21,190 --> 00:20:22,190
During that time,

418
00:20:22,400 --> 00:20:25,400
Bao Kang always invited me over to his house for meals.

419
00:20:25,750 --> 00:20:27,670
Qing Xi's cooking was delicious

420
00:20:28,750 --> 00:20:30,680
and she was very warm and friendly.

421
00:20:33,430 --> 00:20:34,310
Jin Bao,

422
00:20:35,220 --> 00:20:37,190
Bao Kang is always happy when you come.

423
00:20:37,190 --> 00:20:37,850
Otherwise,

424
00:20:37,960 --> 00:20:39,860
he just messes with those herbs all day

425
00:20:39,860 --> 00:20:41,590
and doesn't even say a word to me.

426
00:20:41,590 --> 00:20:42,190
Come.

427
00:20:42,390 --> 00:20:44,910
Bao Kang is exploring the principles of medicine.

428
00:20:44,910 --> 00:20:46,070
He's immersed

429
00:20:46,430 --> 00:20:47,950
in his own world.

430
00:20:49,410 --> 00:20:52,210
He will surely achieve great things in the future.

431
00:20:52,380 --> 00:20:54,620
It's good enough to just gather herbs and sell them to the clinic.

432
00:20:54,620 --> 00:20:56,290
What's the use of researching on his own?

433
00:20:56,290 --> 00:20:57,150
I'm afraid that

434
00:20:57,230 --> 00:21:00,030
he'll become even more withdrawn because of this.

435
00:21:00,230 --> 00:21:01,550
He's not like you, Jin Bao,

436
00:21:01,550 --> 00:21:03,100
racing through the mountains every day

437
00:21:03,100 --> 00:21:04,310
with the sky as the limit.

438
00:21:04,310 --> 00:21:06,710
Your personality is so open and generous too.

439
00:21:06,710 --> 00:21:07,270
How nice.

440
00:21:07,550 --> 00:21:07,950
Come,

441
00:21:08,070 --> 00:21:09,000
let me toast you.

442
00:21:09,200 --> 00:21:09,880
Come.

443
00:21:10,740 --> 00:21:11,180
Come.

444
00:21:15,240 --> 00:21:16,510
After that, Bao Kang rarely

445
00:21:16,510 --> 00:21:18,440
invited me to his house for dinner.

446
00:21:19,270 --> 00:21:20,530
Especially this time,

447
00:21:20,790 --> 00:21:21,790
he broke his leg

448
00:21:22,710 --> 00:21:24,280
and his temperament changed drastically.

449
00:21:24,280 --> 00:21:26,190
He often speaks to Qing Xi coldly

450
00:21:26,220 --> 00:21:27,350
and sarcastically.

451
00:21:28,110 --> 00:21:29,710
He doesn't hit her directly,

452
00:21:30,910 --> 00:21:31,550
but that's because

453
00:21:31,550 --> 00:21:33,280
he's bedridden and can't do it.

454
00:21:34,820 --> 00:21:37,620
Continue talking about what happened last night.

455
00:21:41,030 --> 00:21:41,550
Come.

456
00:21:43,310 --> 00:21:44,710
This is Yunding Red.

457
00:21:45,250 --> 00:21:47,050
I usually can't bear to drink it.

458
00:21:52,000 --> 00:21:52,510
Here.

459
00:21:53,830 --> 00:21:55,630
I don't come to your place often.

460
00:21:56,190 --> 00:21:58,830
Before, it was always with him too.

461
00:22:00,190 --> 00:22:00,830
Yes.

462
00:22:01,680 --> 00:22:02,830
Today, I'm here,

463
00:22:03,830 --> 00:22:05,890
and you're only serving me wild game?

464
00:22:06,080 --> 00:22:09,590
Or do you think I've never had Yunding Red before?

465
00:22:10,350 --> 00:22:10,990
Well…

466
00:22:19,140 --> 00:22:20,200
What are you doing?

467
00:22:22,590 --> 00:22:23,310
Jin Bao,

468
00:22:23,910 --> 00:22:26,170
I don't believe hunting is all you can do.

469
00:22:27,700 --> 00:22:28,310
Wait.

470
00:22:31,910 --> 00:22:33,040
Put your clothes on.

471
00:22:33,730 --> 00:22:35,530
Bao Kang and I are close friends.

472
00:22:35,590 --> 00:22:36,390
By doing this,

473
00:22:36,510 --> 00:22:38,570
what kind of person do you take me for?

474
00:22:44,550 --> 00:22:45,430
That's it.

475
00:22:46,910 --> 00:22:48,110
I concealed it

476
00:22:48,610 --> 00:22:49,700
because I was afraid the rumor

477
00:22:49,700 --> 00:22:51,710
would make life difficult for Bao Kang's wife.

478
00:22:51,710 --> 00:22:52,470
Jin Bao,

479
00:22:53,390 --> 00:22:54,580
from what I've heard,

480
00:22:54,580 --> 00:22:55,980
you are a true gentleman.

481
00:22:56,310 --> 00:22:58,350
I have been righteous since I was a child

482
00:22:58,350 --> 00:22:59,540
and have never changed.

483
00:22:59,540 --> 00:23:00,830
Qing Xi went to your house

484
00:23:00,830 --> 00:23:02,310
and didn't even hold a wine cup?

485
00:23:02,310 --> 00:23:02,830
Yes.

486
00:23:03,590 --> 00:23:04,750
According to your description,

487
00:23:04,750 --> 00:23:06,830
it was less than 15 minutes from when she entered

488
00:23:06,830 --> 00:23:08,230
to when you drove her out.

489
00:23:08,990 --> 00:23:09,720
More or less.

490
00:23:12,030 --> 00:23:12,630
Suo Long,

491
00:23:16,310 --> 00:23:17,710
I'm handing it to you now.

492
00:23:18,060 --> 00:23:18,770
Alright.

493
00:23:23,810 --> 00:23:25,140
Do you know what this is?

494
00:23:26,270 --> 00:23:27,720
It's Wolf Tendon.

495
00:23:28,030 --> 00:23:29,310
Sheriff Lu

496
00:23:29,330 --> 00:23:30,930
brought this from Chang'an.

497
00:23:31,380 --> 00:23:33,390
It's specifically used for detecting lies.

498
00:23:33,390 --> 00:23:35,430
Later, we'll roast it over a fire

499
00:23:35,790 --> 00:23:37,850
and hold it under your nose like this.

500
00:23:37,950 --> 00:23:39,430
If the corner of your mouth twitches,

501
00:23:39,430 --> 00:23:41,150
it means you're lying.

502
00:23:41,190 --> 00:23:42,250
When that happens,

503
00:23:42,550 --> 00:23:44,510
you'll be flogged.

504
00:23:45,380 --> 00:23:47,180
This treasure is very precious.

505
00:23:47,650 --> 00:23:49,470
If it weren't a matter of life and death,

506
00:23:49,470 --> 00:23:51,190
I really wouldn't let him use it.

507
00:23:51,190 --> 00:23:52,520
After all, lighting it once

508
00:23:52,520 --> 00:23:53,950
will use up a lot of it.

509
00:24:17,470 --> 00:24:18,130
Sheriff Lu,

510
00:24:18,200 --> 00:24:18,990
he twitched.

511
00:24:20,830 --> 00:24:21,830
How dare you lie

512
00:24:21,870 --> 00:24:24,130
in front of the newly appointed sheriff?

513
00:24:25,640 --> 00:24:27,150
I'll flog you myself.

514
00:24:27,350 --> 00:24:28,950
I guarantee I'll split your flesh,

515
00:24:28,950 --> 00:24:30,060
snap your tendons, and fracture your brones.

516
00:24:30,060 --> 00:24:31,120
You'll be unable to

517
00:24:31,310 --> 00:24:32,270
go into the mountains

518
00:24:32,270 --> 00:24:33,130
and hunt again.

519
00:24:33,370 --> 00:24:34,870
Your Honor, please spare me!

520
00:24:34,870 --> 00:24:36,270
Your Honor, please spare me!

521
00:24:36,270 --> 00:24:37,430
I didn't kill Qing Xi.

522
00:24:37,430 --> 00:24:39,190
I didn't kill Qing Xi.

523
00:24:40,590 --> 00:24:41,520
Didn't kill her?

524
00:24:41,590 --> 00:24:43,050
Then what did you do to her?

525
00:24:43,430 --> 00:24:43,790
I…

526
00:24:44,830 --> 00:24:45,310
I…

527
00:24:55,230 --> 00:24:56,150
Jin Bao,

528
00:24:56,220 --> 00:24:58,470
not only can you hunt game in the mountains,

529
00:24:58,470 --> 00:25:00,270
but your cooking is aso amazing.

530
00:25:00,670 --> 00:25:02,100
Well, eat more then.

531
00:25:02,870 --> 00:25:03,550
I'm full.

532
00:25:06,750 --> 00:25:07,670
I came today

533
00:25:09,740 --> 00:25:11,340
because I have a favor to ask.

534
00:25:11,670 --> 00:25:12,200
Go ahead.

535
00:25:15,270 --> 00:25:17,870
I want to ask you to persuade him to see a doctor.

536
00:25:18,580 --> 00:25:20,440
Maybe his legs can still be saved.

537
00:25:22,310 --> 00:25:23,150
You also know

538
00:25:25,480 --> 00:25:26,390
that he already

539
00:25:26,430 --> 00:25:27,310
dislikes me.

540
00:25:27,830 --> 00:25:28,590
If I go now…

541
00:25:28,610 --> 00:25:30,370
I really have no other way.

542
00:25:31,380 --> 00:25:32,950
Bao Kang has a withdrawn personality.

543
00:25:32,950 --> 00:25:33,960
You're his only friend

544
00:25:33,960 --> 00:25:35,600
in all of Yunding.

545
00:25:36,510 --> 00:25:37,970
When he was first injured,

546
00:25:38,150 --> 00:25:39,730
I invited doctors to our home,

547
00:25:39,730 --> 00:25:41,260
but he forced them all away.

548
00:25:41,810 --> 00:25:42,470
Now,

549
00:25:42,950 --> 00:25:44,810
I couldn't carry him to the clinic

550
00:25:44,900 --> 00:25:46,180
even if I tried.

551
00:25:47,230 --> 00:25:48,560
You are his best friend.

552
00:25:48,740 --> 00:25:50,150
We can forcefully carry him

553
00:25:50,150 --> 00:25:51,630
to the clinic.

554
00:25:54,530 --> 00:25:56,590
After all, this is a lifelong matter.

555
00:25:58,100 --> 00:25:59,300
If we get to the clinic

556
00:25:59,670 --> 00:26:01,730
and the doctor says it can't be cured,

557
00:26:04,260 --> 00:26:05,660
then I'll accept my fate.

558
00:26:07,270 --> 00:26:08,070
Qing Xi,

559
00:26:10,510 --> 00:26:11,550
you came tonight

560
00:26:13,790 --> 00:26:15,630
just to say this to me?

561
00:26:19,470 --> 00:26:20,100
I know

562
00:26:21,190 --> 00:26:23,320
this puts you in a difficult position.

563
00:26:28,170 --> 00:26:30,390
If Bao Kang really can't

564
00:26:30,880 --> 00:26:32,310
stand up anymore,

565
00:26:34,560 --> 00:26:36,690
do you plan to take care of him for life?

566
00:26:44,710 --> 00:26:45,300
Qing Xi,

567
00:26:45,740 --> 00:26:47,400
Bao Kang doesn't deserve you.

568
00:26:49,570 --> 00:26:50,670
