572
00:26:56,030 --> 00:26:56,960
and insults you,

573
00:26:57,110 --> 00:26:58,110
yet you let him be.

574
00:26:59,070 --> 00:27:00,150
Look at me.

575
00:27:01,350 --> 00:27:02,190
Isn't my life

576
00:27:03,470 --> 00:27:04,750
better than his?

577
00:27:05,580 --> 00:27:06,910
I'll tell you the truth.

578
00:27:07,150 --> 00:27:09,610
Matchmakers come to my door every other day,

579
00:27:09,830 --> 00:27:11,720
